{"word":"H8314 - שָׂרָף - sârâph - saw-rawf' - Fiery","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׂרָף</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sârâph"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>saw-rawf'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Fiery"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கொள்ளி வாய், சேராபீன், அக்கினி சர்ப்பம், கொள்ளிவாய் சர்ப்பம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a serpent, seraph, seraphim"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H8313 - שָׂרַף - sâraph - saw-raf'/8313\">H8313</a>; <i>burning</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>poisonous</i> (serpent); specifically a <i>saraph</i> or symbolical creature (from their copper color): - fiery (serpent), seraph."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4955 - מִשְׂרָפָה - misrâphâh - mis-raw-faw'/4955\">H4955</a>, <a href=\"#/H4956 - מִשְׂרְפֹות מַיִם - Misrᵉphôwth mayim - mis-ref-ohth' mah'-yim/4956\">H4956</a>, <a href=\"#/H5635 - סָרַף - çâraph - saw-raf'/5635\">H5635</a>, <a href=\"#/H8313 - שָׂרַף - sâraph - saw-raf'/8313\">H8313</a>, <a href=\"#/H8314 - שָׂרָף - sârâph - saw-rawf'/8314\">H8314</a>, <a href=\"#/H8315 - שָׂרָף - Sârâph - saw-raf'/8315\">H8315</a>, <a href=\"#/H8316 - שְׂרֵפָה - sᵉrêphâh - ser-ay-faw'/8316\">H8316</a>"}]}